0. Introduction

 XMascot is a program to show pretty Mascot on your X Window System.

1. Installation 

 a. edit config.tmpl
 b. 
    % xmkmf -a
    % make
    % make install
   (% make install.man )

Please refer on-line Manual about options etc.

